  <description><![CDATA[<p>The elegant Grand Hotel San Pietro lies in a quiet corner of <a data-udi="umb://document/919b72992bd64fd4a35a60df994feff6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/919b72992bd64fd4a35a60df994feff6}" title="Taormina Area">Taormina</a> just 15 minutes' walk from the centre of town and surrounded by mature gardens of cypress and palm trees. Stunning views of the sea and coastline can be enjoyed from the pool and the outdoor terraces.</p>
<p>The hotel’s restaurant, Il Giardino degli Ulivi, creates gourmet local specialities and Italian classics which can be enjoyed on the terrace. If you are celebrating a special occasion, we suggest you dine on the Rotonda, a balcony perched high above the Ionian sea offering breathtaking views, where there is only a single table, offering the ultimate romantic setting. To make this occasion even more special, you are able to personalise your own menu.</p>
<p>There is an outdoor swimming pool with sun beds where guests can take a dip and relax in the glorious Sicilian sunshine. La Melarancia pool bar serves an array of drinks and light snacks. Indulge your senses at the Beauty Corner, with a selection of treatments and massages. There is also a gym for guests who like to keep active their holiday. </p>]]></description>
