  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Executive Rooms</strong> are approximately between 23-25m² and offer views over Taormina. The rooms is set up with a double bed but twin beds can be set up upon request. These rooms have either a private bath or a shower and amenities include, air conditioning, TV, minibar, safe and hairdryer.</p>
<p>The <strong>Deluxe Rooms</strong> have been furnished in a traditional Sicilian style and have beautiful sea views that can be enjoyed on the private balcony. These rooms are approximately, between 25-30m². Call to book this room. </p>
<p><strong>Garden Suites</strong> are located on the first floor and are approximately, between 35-40m². These rooms offer a spacious living area and bedroom and have a private terrace that has views of the hotels gardens. Call to book this room. </p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are luxurious and spacious at approximately, 38m² and have a bedroom and a living area equipped with a table and chairs and a sofa bed. These rooms are located on the first and second floor and have a private balcony with stunning sea views where you can enjoy breakfast or even dinner. Call to book this room. </p>
<p>The <strong>Regal Suite</strong> is located on the top floor and the views expand across the whole of Naxos Bay and you can see Mount Etna too on a clear day! This room and its views are splendid and offers so much space at approximately, 88m² with two bedrooms, two bathrooms, a pretty lounge and two furnished balconies.  Call to book this room. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
